data.title: Summary of Criminal Prosecutions - U. S. District Courts
meta_keywords: Support Delivery of Services > Public Affairs > Official Information Dissemination > Public Information & Outreach > Provide Public Information
data.meta_description: This page provides links to various Federal District Courts of the United States used in the Summary of Criminal Prosecutions.
data.text:
This page provides links to various Federal District Courts of the United States used in the Summary of Criminal Prosecutions. States may have more than one district, these districts are broken down by geographic location. You may search the Summary of Criminal Prosecutions for cases in a specific Federal District Court.

In addition, some EPA Criminal Enforcement offices' area of responsibility is determined by the geographic area serviced by a specific Federal District Court.
